{"title":"饭厅的墙上","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":1,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭厅的墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人望着墙上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着红纸盖着绿纸的墙上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了手中的馒头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与桌上的菜碗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已渐渐失去热气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"议论的声音扩散着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一百台布机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织着气愤与舍不得的细纱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少心血与钱财浪费掉了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几年来我们不愿迟到一分钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿出一匹次布。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而贵重的空气压缩机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年只用了一次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一个精强力壮的汉子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被关在寂寞的仓库中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让尘土陪伴长长的岁月。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么要买它？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要的东西又这么迟缓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看石磨的经历吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修厂房，安装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无休止的翻工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不能磨玉米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱和时间流走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像呼唤不回来的河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浆纱车间只得忍痛地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用富强粉浆纱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待又等待。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁来算算这笔细账？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人心疼的还有铁辊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万五千个！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人曾为它昼夜忙碌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根掏空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根灌铅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（铅是从安东运来的）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根用焊锡补空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根磨光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后，没有用！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像废物一样地堆着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆着的还有信号灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个五年计划也用不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的仓库呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了取之不尽的宝库了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫帚也像森林。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨迹未干的大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被盖上了，盖上了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爆破队”，“突击队”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像精明的侦察兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芝麻与西瓜都不放过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向浪费开火！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠消灭浪费吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也消灭浪费的保姆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那使人厌恶的官气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请围在墙边的人们让开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的大字报抬来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快贴上去！快贴上去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多好呵，请看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是找窍门，出主意的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是医生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钱，一秒钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都痛惜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作得对，细纱甲二组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们今年又不领工作服了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破了就缝补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有富余的就给别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心灵震荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟上去，跟上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引火烧身不要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要祖国在社会主义路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞奔得更快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越多的人望着墙上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚吃过饭的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把大字报抬来了……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}